---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pricing — LeadFair"
  description="Simple pricing for your business's AI. Three plans by team size — everything included at every tier. No feature gates, no hidden fees."
>
  <!-- Founding Member Banner -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-secondary-500 text-white py-4 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold">Founding Member Pricing — Lock in these rates. They won't last forever.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-blue py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="blob blob-blue w-72 h-72 -top-20 -right-20"></div>
    <div class="blob blob-green w-56 h-56 bottom-0 left-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid opacity-40"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-6">
        <span class="gradient-text-blue-green">Simple Pricing.</span><br/>
        <span class="gradient-text-blue-green">Everything Included.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-text-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Every plan includes every feature — AI receptionist, automations, visibility, and company companion. Pick the plan that fits your team size.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="shimmer-line"></div>

  <!-- Pricing Tiers -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Solo -->
        <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover card-glow-blue">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1">Solo</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light text-sm">For one-person businesses</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-5xl font-extrabold">$199</span>
              <span class="text-text-light text-lg">/mo</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">AI Receptionist (24/7 call answering)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Automations & custom workflows</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Visibility optimization</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Company Companion</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">1 team member</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="group w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary-500 text-white py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-primary-600 transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg btn-scale">
              Get Started
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Team (Popular) -->
        <div class="relative gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover card-glow-green ring-2 ring-secondary-500">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-secondary-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Most Popular</div>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1">Team</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light text-sm">For small teams (2-5 people)</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-5xl font-extrabold">$399</span>
              <span class="text-text-light text-lg">/mo</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">AI Receptionist (24/7 call answering)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Automations & custom workflows</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Visibility optimization</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Company Companion</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Up to 5 team members</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="group w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-secondary-500 text-white py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-secondary-600 transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg btn-scale">
              Get Started
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Business -->
        <div class="gradient-border rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover card-glow-orange">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1">Business</h3>
              <p class="text-text-light text-sm">For growing teams (6-15 people)</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-5xl font-extrabold">$599</span>
              <span class="text-text-light text-lg">/mo</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">AI Receptionist (24/7 call answering)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Automations & custom workflows</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Visibility optimization</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Company Companion</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="icon-box icon-box-green w-5 h-5 rounded shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm text-text-light">Up to 15 team members</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="group w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-accent-500 text-white py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-accent-600 transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg btn-scale">
              Get Started
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 mt-10 text-sm text-text-lighter">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/></svg>
          <span>Your data is encrypted & never shared</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          <span>Cancel anytime — no contracts</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-secondary-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z"/></svg>
          <span>Secure payments via Stripe</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-text-lighter text-sm mt-4">Need more than 15 people? <a href="/contact" class="text-primary-500 underline hover:text-primary-600">Get in touch</a> and we'll work something out.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="shimmer-line"></div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-warm">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">What's included in every plan?</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">Everything. AI receptionist, automations, visibility optimization, and company companion. The only difference between plans is team size — the number of people who can log in and use LeadFair.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Can I cancel anytime?</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">Yes. No contracts, no cancellation fees. If LeadFair isn't working for you, cancel anytime from your account settings.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Is there a free trial?</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">Not yet — but you can try our free Business Diagnostic or Visibility Audit to see exactly what LeadFair would do for your business before signing up.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Are there any hidden fees or usage limits?</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">No. The price you see is the price you pay. No per-call charges, no overage fees, no usage meters. We keep it simple.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">How long does setup take?</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">Most businesses are up and running within a day. Sign up, tell LeadFair about your business, and it configures itself. The more detail you give it, the better it works.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Is my business data safe?</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">Yes. Your data is encrypted at rest and in transit, stored securely, and never sold or shared with third parties. It's never used to train AI models for other customers. Only you and your team can access it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 card-hover">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">What does "founding member pricing" mean?</h3>
          <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">We're in early access. If you sign up now, you lock in the current rates — even when prices go up later. Think of it as a thank-you for being early.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="shimmer-line"></div>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-dark text-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-dark opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="blob blob-blue w-96 h-96 -top-40 -right-40 opacity-20"></div>
    <div class="blob blob-green w-72 h-72 -bottom-20 -left-20 opacity-15"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 text-center space-y-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
        Ready to Get Started?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Pick a plan and put your business on autopilot. Or try a free tool first — no signup required.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center pt-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="group bg-accent-500 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-accent-600 transition-all text-lg shadow-glow-orange btn-scale flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          Get Started
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/tools/business-diagnostic" class="group bg-white text-dark px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all text-lg shadow-xl btn-scale flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          Try the Free Diagnostic
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
